            &nbsp;<span class="label label-default">OS X 10.9以降で動作します。</span></a>      </p>

      <p>
        <a href="https://github.com/tekezo/ShowyEdge/blob/master/LICENSE.md" target="_blank">
        <img src="/img/icon/license-public-domain.svg" alt="Public Domain" />
        </a>
      </p>

